metadata.name: SHIESTY SEASON: SPRING
metadata.description:
SPRING EDITION:

The title Shiesty Season represented Pooh Shiesty claiming his time. He was a new artist that was quickly rising up the charts and becoming one of the next biggest superstars of our generation. He wanted to represent through a series of seasonal covers that although he was claiming his “Season” that it wasn’t just for one “Season”. It wasn’t just Winter or Spring or Summer or Fall. It was all of them. He was here to stay.
